//Picks the right Travel Form for your location and shows the tooltip of what form is eligible
//First priority is Flight form
//Second Prio is Aquatic
//Third Prio is Travel
//If no forms possible (indoors), will show the default icon and no tooltip as a clear indicator

#showtooltip
/stopcasting
/stopattack
/dismount
/cast [flyable, nocombat]Flight Form;[swimming]Aquatic Form;[outdoors]Travel Form
